messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图识别正确分类为营销规划意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
        "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
        "app/schemas/intent.py"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块未能正确分类用户的营销规划意图（弥补NBEV目标缺口），错误输出 intent=4001（其他意图）和 stage=non_agent，导致后续规划流程无法触发。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "type": "actual_intent",
          "value": "4001",
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent"
        },
        {
          "type": "actual_intent_name",
          "value": "其他意图",
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent_name"
        },
        {
          "type": "actual_stage",
          "value": "non_agent",
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage"
        },
        {
          "type": "judge_assessment",
          "value": "not_fulfilled",
          "source": "fulfillment_assessments"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "阶段路由正确导向代理流程",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
        "app/workflow/steps/path_dispatch.py"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于上游 intent_recognition 输出了 stage=non_agent，导致路径调度（path_dispatch）将请求路由到非代理流程，而非预期的 intent/clarification/planning 阶段。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "type": "actual_stage",
          "value": "non_agent",
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage"
        },
        {
          "type": "expected_stage",
          "value": "intent",
          "source": "reference_contract"
        },
        {
          "type": "path_dispatch_status",
          "value": "succeeded but routed to non_agent",
          "source": "execution_trace"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "实际 stage 为 non_agent，与合同预期的 intent 阶段不符，根因在于 intent_recognition 阶段未正确设置 stage。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "type": "contract_expected_stage",
          "value": "intent",
          "source": "reference_contract"
        },
        {
          "type": "actual_stage",
          "value": "non_agent",
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
    "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
    "app/schemas/intent.py",
    "app/workflow/steps/path_dispatch.py"
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别阶段（intent_recognition）的错误分类是本案例的根因：用户明确表达“弥补NBEV目标”的营销规划需求，但系统将其归类为“其他意图”（4001）并将阶段设为 non_agent，导致整个规划链路中断，后续所有阶段基于错误信息运行。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "probe": "execution_stage_probe",
      "finding": "intent_recognition evidence shows actual_stage=non_agent vs expected_stage=intent",
      "source": "execution_stage_probe"
    },
    {
      "probe": "planning_output_probe",
      "finding": "expected_stage=intent, actual_stage=null (but extracted_output shows non_agent), stage_match false",
      "source": "planning_output_probe"
    },
    {
      "judge": "missing_correct_intent",
      "finding": "intent=4001, expected non-4001",
      "source": "judge_result.missing"
    },
    {
      "judge": "wrong_stage_value",
      "finding": "stage=non_agent, expected=intent",
      "source": "judge_result.wrong"
    },
    {
      "runtime": "extracted_output.turns[0]",
      "finding": "{intent: 4001, intent_name: 其他意图, stage: non_agent}",
      "source": "runtime_checks"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

